i3wm Keybindings Cheat Sheet
=============================

 = Super/Windows key

## General
+Return          start ghostty terminal
+q               kill focused window
+Shift+c         reload configuration file
+Shift+r         restart i3 inplace
+l               lock screen (blur)
+Shift+e         exit/power menu

## Application Launchers
+d               application menu (rofi)
+t               window switcher (rofi)
+w               launch Firefox
Print            screenshot (flameshot)

## Window Focus
+j               focus left
+k               focus down
+b               focus up
+o               focus right
+Left/Down/Up/Right   (arrow key alternatives)

## Move Focused Window
+Shift+j         move left
+Shift+k         move down
+Shift+b         move up
+Shift+o         move right
+Shift+Left/Down/Up/Right   (arrow key alternatives)

## Layout
+h               split horizontal
+v               split vertical
+f               fullscreen toggle
+s               layout stacking
+g               layout tabbed
+e               layout toggle split

## Floating
+Shift+space     toggle tiling/floating
+space           toggle focus tiling/floating
+mouse drag      move floating window

## Workspaces
+1-0             switch to workspace 1-10
+Shift+1-0       move container to workspace 1-10
+Tab             next workspace
+Shift+Tab       previous workspace
+Shift+n         open new empty workspace

## Resize Mode
+r               enter resize mode
  Arrow keys     resize window
  Enter/Escape   exit resize mode

## Focus
+a               focus parent container

## Multimedia
XF86Audio keys   volume up/down/mute (with OSD)
+XF86Audio keys  granular volume (1% steps)
XF86Brightness   screen brightness up/down
XF86AudioMicMute mic mute toggle
XF86AudioPlay    play/pause
XF86AudioNext    next track
XF86AudioPrev    previous track

## Other
+p               switch audio port (headphones)
+Shift+p         power profiles menu (rofi)
